CL CONNECTION HEALTH SCALE VERSION 1:
        Designed to measure the strength of CL professional connections.

        0 - never have interacted with
        -----------------------------------------------------
        1 - physically interacted with once, no follow back
        2 - physically interacted with more than once, no follow back
        3 - never have physically interacted, but follows back
        -----------------------------------------------------
        4 - physically interacted once, follow back
        5 - physically interacted more than once, follow back
        -----------------------------------------------------
        6 - physically interacted over 5 times
        7 - physically interacted over 10 times

KL CONNECTION RELEVANCY SCALE VERSION 1:
        Designed to measure the relevancy of the people in your circle.

        0 - never have interacted with 
        -----------------------------------------------------
        1 - time frame: over a year
        2 - time frame: 1 year
        3 - time frame: 6 months
        4 - time frame: 3 months
        5 - time frame: 1 month
        6 - time frame: 1 week